467
00:20:51,960 --> 00:20:53,503
Otra vez con eso.

468
00:20:53,503 --> 00:20:54,337


469
00:20:54,337 --> 00:20:57,007
¡De ninguna manera! ¡No permitiré que trabajes!

470
00:20:57,007 --> 00:20:57,132


471
00:20:57,132 --> 00:20:59,759
