00:23:41,671 --> 00:23:42,756
Ya me voy.

518
00:23:42,005 --> 00:23:42,756

519
00:23:42,756 --> 00:23:43,923
¡Espera, Yawara!

520
00:23:44,466 --> 00:23:47,594
